    <statement><p>Factor the given polynomial.</p>
<p><m>{8t^{4}-24t^{3}+28t^{2}}=</m> <fillin characters="19" name="AnSwEr0001"/></p>
</statement>
    <answer>
      <p>
        <m>4t^{2}\mathopen{}\left(2t^{2}-6t+7\right)</m>
      </p>
    </answer>
    <solution><p>The greatest common factor is <m>4t^2</m>, so we can factor the polynomial as follows:</p>
<p><m>{8t^{4}-24t^{3}+28t^{2}}={4t^{2}\mathopen{}\left(2t^{2}-6t+7\right)}</m></p>
</solution>
